*version 1
**memory
**control and integer instructions
**assembly parser
**assembly lexer
**binary generator
**simulation (every instruction takes 1 tick)
**GUI

*version 2
**floating point instructions
**trip/trap
**break points
**break conditions

*version 3
**virtual physical addressing
**clock-cycle accurate simulation
**editable per-instruction cost
**cost reporting

*version 4
**hardware simulation
***eg, VGA, console, other I/O
***hard disk image
***ISO image
***extensible
